Some Of The Hong Kong Airlines Flights Cancelled Due to Typhoon Saudelor Adv: 
Aug 07, 2015 Adv: 
Due to Typhoon Saudelor, some Hong Kong Airlinesâ€™ flights operating on today and tomorrow will be cancelled: 
7 August: HX282 Hong Kong to Taipei HX283 Taipei to Hong Kong HX284 Hong Kong to Taipei 
8 August: HX285 Taipei to Hong Kong 
Passengers are advised to check the latest Flight Status on the websites of Hong Kong Airport and Hong Kong Airlines, or contact our Call Center. Hong Kong Airlines Call Center: Hong Kong: (852) 3916 3666 / Mainland China: 950715.
